### Health Check - Verify the application is running
GET {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/actuator/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get All Expenses - Returns list of all expenses (reactive endpoint with coroutines)
GET {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Expense by ID - Returns a specific expense
GET {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create Expense - Create a new expense (amount in cents)
POST {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Groceries",
  "amount": 5000,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2026-01-19T15:30:00Z"
}

###

