###

### Get Non-Existing Expense - Should return 404
GET {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/999
Accept: application/json

###

### Update Expense - Update an existing expense (all fields optional)
PUT {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Updated Groceries",
  "amount": 6000,
  "category": "Food",
  "date": "2026-01-19T15:30:00Z"
}

###

### Update Expense - Partial update (only amount)
PUT {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 7500
}

###

### Delete Expense - Soft delete an expense
DELETE {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Trigger Sync - Manually trigger sync operation
POST {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/sync
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Device ID - Returns the current device ID
GET {{ExpensesApiUrl}}/api/expenses/device-id
Accept: application/json

